des:
Rock Fm 89.2 Limassol ‘’Light Rock Less Talk’’
Limassol, a city with a strong, overwhelming personality. A city that combines the easy-going summer feeling of Paphos with the strong social life of Nicosia and the constant artistic nature of Limassol itself.

Bearing in mind that this permeates every aspect of Limassol’s every day life, Rock Fm 89.2 aims to be the daily soundtrack to everyone in Limassol with great music and less talking.

With 15 years of radio experience and a hunger for new challenges, Rock FM is now launching a brand new schedule format specially tailored for Rock Fm 89.2 Limassol with our motto and mission statement “Light Rock Less Talk’’ leading the way as we believe it should be done: less talk, more music!

Rock Fm 89.2 promises to be an explosive combination that will change the way you listen to radio. All you have to do is tune in on 89.2 and let the music do the talking.
